 into her hard drive and sent itself to practically everyone who's ever wri=
tten to her. When I checked there was an EMail with an attachment involving=
 something she sent me quite a while ago. As a precaution I suggest that NO=
BODY open any Emails with attachments until I find out for sure if my syste=
m was corrupted. I hope I deleted it on time. If I deleted it sorry about t=
he scare, if not then I hope it doesn't wipe out our little world.

C.Wolf
